org.shared.array

Class AbstractRealArray<R extends AbstractRealArray<R,C>,C extends AbstractComplexArray<C,R>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.shared.array.ProtoArray<T,double[],E>
      • org.shared.array.AbstractArray<R,C,R,Double>
        • org.shared.array.AbstractRealArray<R,C>
  • Type Parameters:
    R - the real array type.
    C - the complex array type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, Array<R,Double>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RealArray

    public abstract class AbstractRealArray<R extends AbstractRealArray<R,C>,C extends AbstractComplexArray<C,R>>
extends AbstractArray<R,C,R,Double>
    An abstract base class for arrays of real values.
